						               													<description>A fantasy dice game where 2 or more players control the armies of Sorroah using the forbidden artefacts: the BattleBones.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;BattleBones sees players take on the role of a CleroMancer one of the MageCaste who use ancient Artefacts of great power to control the armies of the land. Through the use of these BattleBones, warriors and heroes are summoned to the field of battle, where great battlelines are created with which to attack the enemy.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;These BattleBones are represented by special engraved dice, each face showing one of the elements of the army:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each turn players roll their dice and lay out their battlelines, placing the dice in the order they wish to play them. Dice are then compared in a rock-paper-scissors fashion with the winning dice able to continue the fight. The losing dice are killed and removed to the Graveyard.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;It's a great little game suited to killing time between wargames, waiting for a table to come available at the club, or down the pub with your friends.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
